Casterbane Shot		CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat.Grit	PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Point-Blank Shot,Precise Shot			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Amateur Gunslinger],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Grit,Gunslinger ~ Grit]													PRETEXT:Prerequisites: Amateur Gunslingeruc or the grit class feature, Point-Blank Shot, Precise Shot, base attack bonus +4.						PRETOTALAB:4	DESC:Life in the Mana Wastes, where magic has unpredictable and often fatal effects, has taught you to disable spellcasters with your firearms.					SOURCEPAGE:p.17	BENEFIT:If you ready a ranged attack with a firearm to attack a spellcaster when he begins casting a spell and successfully hit your opponent, you can expend 1 grit point to increase the target's concentration check DC for being injured while casting by 5.
